  "title": "CCTV Project Engineer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><ul><li>Install, test, commission, and program security equipment in compliance with company policies and standards.</li><li>Manage projects to ensure successful completion.</li><li>Provide technical support and assistance to Sales and other departments.</li><li>Troubleshoot and resolve issues related to security systems.</li><li>Conduct on-site training sessions for clients.</li><li>Utilize AutoCAD to design security systems and create building diagrams.</li><li>Maintain a high level of knowledge in security concepts.</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirement:</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum Diploma in Electronic, Computer, Automation, or Mechanical Engineering or relevant</li><li>Minimum with 2 year working experience in CCTV/ Security Industry</li></ul><p>To submit your application, please apply online to <a href=\"mailto:apply@rn-care.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>apply@rn-care.com </strong></a>or call +(65) <a href=\"tel:6513 5697\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>6513 5697</strong></a> for private and confidential discussion.</p><p>Your interest will be treated with the strictest of confidence. We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified or contacted.</p><p><strong>RN Care Pte. Ltd</strong><br /><strong>EA License No: 17C8900</strong></p>",
